#~ msgid ""
#~ "The <guilabel>Sending</guilabel> tab provides a list of ways to send "
#~ "messages. The first item in the list is the default way to send messages. "
#~ "Using the <guibutton>Add...</guibutton> button you can fill in the "
#~ "<guilabel>Name</guilabel> field with a descriptive name (&eg; "
#~ "<userinput>My Mail Account</userinput>). Click the <guibutton>Create and "
